      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but honestly it just feels like a waste of meds if the skin is already clear. mcm doctors just give everyone a standard 10 days regardless of how fast they heal. if the bacteria are already dead, isn't it actually healthier for my body to just stop instead of loading up on more drugs for no reason?",
