      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see why the \"risk\" of it coming back is worth the side effects i'm having. my stomach is already super upset from these pills and i hate feeling nauseous. if the infection looks 100% gone, what are the actual chances it really comes back just because i stopped a few days early? it feels like an unnecessary risk to keep taking them if i'm already fine.",
